# Keep secrets, VCS, and caches out of the Cloud Build upload.
# The Dockerfile only COPYs requirements.txt, app/, entrypoint.sh, so this is
# mostly to ensure .env (secrets) never leaves the box and to trim upload size.
# NOTE: deliberately NOT excluding app/data/*.db - the Dockerfile re-COPYs app/,
# so excluding them would change the image vs the current prod build. Prod uses
# Postgres (EDGES_DATABASE_URL) but we keep image parity to be safe.
.env
.env.*
.git
.gitignore
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
scripts/_*.txt
